{"tid":2225163,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"太古城太湖閣一樓某住戶真愛共！","createTime":"2020-10-01T05:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T05:16:46.000Z","uid":127922,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"718fef667bc13fdc0e6140a30ab489e5160edf06","tid":2225163,"uid":127922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"值得表揚！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vnsy7nz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvnsy7nz.jpg&h=46a3eb98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67de616a7ad98b68445bf34b35981fd3253a7726","tid":2225163,"uid":45213,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"住咁低都咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadaf986f50190d3ea9a490afd15aa46f984bd8f","tid":2225163,"uid":254594,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"67de616a7ad98b68445bf34b35981fd3253a7726","tid":2225163,"uid":45213,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"住咁低都咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"驚咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15d2bfb811dcd1fc756153f98825d2afeea14f9","tid":2225163,"uid":127922,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"67de616a7ad98b68445bf34b35981fd3253a7726","tid":2225163,"uid":45213,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"住咁低都咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"有人Care就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛共好波"},{"pid":"8e4857aaaddcf4e65313b1be58ca9c34739632ab","tid":2225163,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49341f207cd6e08a7f065547bdaa883c36ac0a1e","tid":2225163,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>【太古城血案】遭咬甩耳趙家賢清醒 兩男子重傷危殆</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3500492/org/6249c5ad8348b68a18de9b90f9598fd2.jpg/FVN4bwrGCGtT7y1slA6vPb1xPPFF0n8hUvDlG1Lw5Rs?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3500492%2Forg%2F6249c5ad8348b68a18de9b90f9598fd2.jpg%2FFVN4bwrGCGtT7y1slA6vPb1xPPFF0n8hUvDlG1Lw5Rs%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=4f43dcd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前太古城發生血案，該區區議員、民主黨趙家賢疑在混亂中被一名灰衣男子咬甩左耳部分耳朵，其後送往東區醫院救治。多名民主派議員到東區醫院探望他，民主黨立法會議員涂謹申指趙現時清醒，但未知斷耳能否駁回。趙又呼籲太古街坊今晚不要為他聚集，聲稱「擔心警方濫用暴力」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3500339/org/9d35b5ef75d0fd0b8ec5bab6280b1d71.jpg/p0A9Q4y6WLRDIVhqDSgU9_SDLmTApg4FE_tY5RP7WOU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3500339%2Forg%2F9d35b5ef75d0fd0b8ec5bab6280b1d71.jpg%2Fp0A9Q4y6WLRDIVhqDSgU9_SDLmTApg4FE_tY5RP7WOU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6aa1263c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫院管理局發言人指，太古城事件中有五名傷者被送到東區醫院，年齡介乎29至48歲。其中兩名男子情況危殆，一男一女情況嚴重，另一名男子情況穩定。據了解，情況嚴重的男子是趙家賢；至於危殆兩男，一是頸部大量出血的受襲男子，另一是涉施襲後遭多人圍毆「私了」的灰衣男，他同樣頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，案件暫列「襲擊致他人受傷」，三人被捕。"},{"pid":"e973ca181465d2eef589f3bd1a37cfbb997fc663","tid":2225163,"uid":89869,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dadaf986f50190d3ea9a490afd15aa46f984bd8f","tid":2225163,"uid":254594,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"67de616a7ad98b68445bf34b35981fd3253a7726","tid":2225163,"uid":45213,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"住咁低都咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"驚咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"可能有人請佢飲咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},